# User Story

As a person with a hectic schedule involved in a number of projects,
I want to see all my pending tasks  and deadlines for different projects in one place,
In order to manage my time more effectively and increase productivity.

# Instruction
Users can create an account, log in and organise their tasks in certain projects.
Users will be able add due dates to the tasks and these tasks will be sorted by due date in order to prioritise them and increase productivity.
